metadata.description:
270 FRAMES: GENESIS.
The first edition of the 270 FRAMES collection, each NFT contains 270 frames of unique and captivating code-driven art.

Ownership of a piece of this collection will entitle the holder to future access to the 270 FRAMES eco-system including priority WL on future editions of 270 FRAMES and access to the holders only membership (tba). 

We look forward to welcoming you to our world of 270 FRAMES!
metadata.name: 270 FRAMES: GENESIS #1
